{"tid":1020682,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"今朝趕時間返工, 撞到個男仔..","createTime":"2019-02-13T18:40:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-14T10:38:15.000Z","uid":123991,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"aae3379dd0146b883d03bcda27e16e8882398a15","tid":1020682,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T18:40:02.000Z","msg":"今朝趕時間返工<br />\n就遲到果陣拎咗個麵包就一路跑一咬返公司..<br />\n落到apm附近個街口<br />\n轉灣睇唔到唔小心撞到個男仔<br />\n我失平衡趺咗落地<br />\n諗住今次實畀人開年都似 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知畀我撞到果個男仔扶返我起身仲問我有冇事<br />\n佢真係好 warm, 果一刻都唔知點反應好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n條件反射淨係知返工就遲到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\non99 冇留低 contact 我就走左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家好想搵返佢過情人節 <br />\n唔知有冇機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00b60931d23be781dc94b7d5425763d158e677dc","tid":1020682,"uid":8345,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T18:41:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c5f4bf642b9dac6f8e5de8e7745249765af7bc8a","tid":1020682,"uid":111965,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T18:42:29.000Z","msg":"你有冇理過麵包既感受"},{"pid":"b31dd1113b454d83d0b3b9edd86701b25b7f6660","tid":1020682,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c5f4bf642b9dac6f8e5de8e7745249765af7bc8a","tid":1020682,"uid":111965,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T18:42:29.000Z","msg":"你有冇理過麵包既感受"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T18:43:05.000Z","msg":"咬咗一兩啖 就跌咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10449c7c5b46c7a716700b34971f30dd4c6af83b","tid":1020682,"uid":196126,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T18:43:45.000Z","msg":"真係惨, 情人節恨仔恨到有幻覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"823af0fdb0e1900bd1b475a